{"tid":292490,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[發達大計] 震驚700萬人的賺錢大法, 你肯定從來沒想到賺錢原來是那麼易","createTime":"2017-06-21T12:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T14:38:48.000Z","uid":79481,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc125768b31581300c169f906872784ccac9c7e","tid":292490,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"我知做左標題黨 睇完如果覺得唔work再腐皮我<br />\n<br />\n我知道以我能力應該做唔黎 所以我唔怕share俾大家 OK開始<br />\n<br />\n岩岩諗到樣野 希望我講得明白個概念俾大家聽<br />\n<br />\n1. 放一架裝滿貨既大貨車係合法泊車既街邊<br />\n<br />\n2. 整一個網上付費平台, 顧客於網上平台選購及付費<br />\n<br />\n3. 顧客到貨車向職員提供證明物件<br />\n<br />\n4. 顧客取貨並離去<br />\n<br />\n貨車的角色只是&quot;送貨&quot;, 貨車與顧客完全沒有直接交易, 也沒有買賣<br />\n<br />\n本身我諗住貨幣係用bitcoin, 一黎transaction比較容易, 二黎唔需要俾手續費, 三黎究竟bitcoin係咪一種認可貨幣都係問題<br />\n<br />\n但之後諗諗下其實只要係電子貨幣都ok<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇? 呢個方法有冇觸犯咩法律? 又或者可唔可行?"},{"pid":"5bbe69c2a0423925af7dc52f48c7264119605551","tid":292490,"uid":43760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"問律師真係咁難？"},{"pid":"c66e90f7315f9e154ab03f1b9a9522dfc9223870","tid":292490,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"520dfa5508a273e5953056b3fb0a9046d3f4e733","tid":292490,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"睇到係咪認可貨幣就已經知樓主...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fca9bd975ed3436849f0b6f5db1b5d86685c5a","tid":292490,"uid":46910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"同送件貨去locker 自己領冇分別"},{"pid":"20ae63dd1ea6184f5746820ce933a2eb713b17fa","tid":292490,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a86568800203cb73d6e74ad161e2ffddca9f6c","tid":292490,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"